Programming language are classified into various Programming Paradigm  (Programming Paradigm - Different ways to write the code)
Such as 
1. Procedural
2. Object Oriented 
3. Imperative 

All the programming lanaguage are classified based on their features

For Example :
Python support mulitple programming paradigm (Imperative , Object Oriented , Procedural , Functional)

procedular Paradigm - To build a program step by step instruction is executed
- It has reusable Block of statements

Problem -
1. It makes the program difficult
2. It defines the varaibles globally
